OL,3,CTen babies die in fire at Indian
OL,4,Chospital
OL,6,F"We will identify those responsible
OL,7,Ffor this tragedy and take strict
OL,8,Faction. The government stands with
OL,9,Ffamilies during this difficult time,"
OL,10,FBrajesh Pathak, the deputy chief
OL,11,Fminister of the state, said.
OL,13,FHe added that DNA tests were being
OL,14,Fcarried out after which the bodies of
OL,15,Fthe babies will be handed over to
OL,16,Ftheir families.
