OL,3,CTen babies die in fire at Indian
OL,4,Chospital
OL,6,F"If the safety alarm had worked, we
OL,7,Fcould have acted sooner and saved more
OL,8,Flives," said Naresh Kumar, a parent
OL,9,Fwho lost his baby.
OL,11,FMr Pathak, the state official, said
OL,12,Fthe hospital's fire safety systems
OL,13,Fwere last inspected in February,
OL,14,Ffollowed by a mock drill in June.
